Package de.payleven.inappsdk.listeners

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AddPaymentInstrumentListener
    Listener that notifies when the payment instrument was added successfully or not.
    EditPaymentInstrumentListener
    Listener that notifies when a payment instrument was edited, based on the response from the backend.
    GetPaymentInstrumentsListener
    Listener for payment instruments retrieval from backend.
    RegistrationListener
    Listener that reaction on registration result, returning either an instance of the PaylevenInAppClient in case the registration is successful or a Throwable in case the registration fails
    RemovePaymentInstrumentListener
    Listener that notifies when a payment instrument was removed from a use case based on the response from the backend In case of failure, a throwable containing the reason will be give as parameter
    SetPaymentInstrumentsOrderListener
    Listener for setting the order of payment instruments In case of failure, a throwable containing the reason will be give as parameter
